name: nena crouch
text: Not anything nice to say so I will keep it to myself. But I will say that these schools are nothing like they are tried to portrayed to be.

name: Barnes Gregory
text: Student beatings are permitted in this school district from k12 through maturing high school students by school teachers and administrators. This district needs to be sued again and again regardless of the outcome. There are no safeguards and no checks n place, and no limits to this physical and psychological abuse of young people. Most places in the USA have long outlawed this violence but here it is being promoted.

name: Vicki Kelley
text: Friendly group.

name: carol costello
text: I called Sadie’s and received a text for an appointment the following week.  Autumn was kind, professional and genuinely happy to see my dog, who was not of the same thinking.  Benny came out looking like a new dog and, for the first time, was well behaved while being groomed.  Drop off and pickup were simple and future appointments were discussed after I was given time to be sure I was satisfied.  We will make Sadie’s our new grooming destination.  Thank you Autumn and all the staff at Sadie’s.

resp.text: Awe thank you so much, Benny is super sweet and very easy to groom, we really love him!!!!!

name: Beth Main
text: Awesome job we will definitely be back they were very patient with Bandit for his 1st haircut

resp.text: Awe thank you, he was a good boy 🐶🐶🐶

name: Richard Poulson
text: Great owner and staff, very friendly and caring with the animals and their owners. Highly recommend!

name: Wesley Paradise
text: Fantastic groomer.  Only place I take my pet.

resp.text: Awe thank you, I love my baby girl

name: Leah Ehrlich
text: We took our 15 week old doodle puppy to Sadie's Dog House for grooming. Being new to having a dog we needed lots of guidance. They were kind, helpful and knowledgeable about the best way to groom Yoffi. They were so gentle and sweet with our baby. We highly recommend them! Yoffi looks amazing too!

name: Celeste Cody
text:
Sadie's Dog House L.L.C completely rocked the customer service and good groom categories today.

This old man got his first full groom and looks amazing. On top of that they met me AFTER HOURS due to some family medical issues and made sure our fur family was all home before bed time.

Highly recommend 12/10. Will return again.

resp.text: And we would do it all over again for those babies and the wonderful owner☺️

name: Danny & Lisa Stokes
text:
Wonderful group of Ladies! Just moved to the area so our first time to use. Helpful and kind to my fur babies and us humans too! Great job grooming and taking care of my
Pups! Highly recommend!!

resp.text: Awe!!! Thank you they are very loving babies 🐕🐕🐕🐕
